Rectangle

                 int iAbsoluteStart,

                 String iIsoformID,
                 int iColor)
Instantiates a new Rectangle.

Parameters:
iScaledXCoord - the left value of the X coordinate of the rectangle
iScaledYCoord - the top value of the Y coordinate of the rectangle
iScaledLength - the scaled length of the rectangle
iScaledHeight - the scaled height of the rectangle
iAbsoluteStart - the genomic start coordinate of the region defined by the rectangle (inclusive)
iAbsoluteEnd - the genomic end coordinate of the region defined by the rectangle (inclusive)
iIsoformID - the ID of the MRNA that this rectangle is a part of
iColor - the color of the rectangle
